abstract: Experts say a new round of talks, and the government’s intervention, are almost certain to delay a settlement Google was eager to see ratified quickly.
snippet: Experts say a new round of talks, and the government’s intervention, are almost certain to delay a settlement Google was eager to see ratified quickly.
lead_paragraph: For months, Google and its partners in a class-action settlement that would allow the company to create a vast digital library appeared unmoved by a rising tide of opposition.

headline.main: Google Working to Revise Digital Books Settlement
headline.print_headline: Google Working to Revise Digital Books Settlement

abstract: Obama administration stiffs Fox News and jumps in governor’s race. Meet the new boss.
snippet: Obama administration stiffs Fox News and jumps in governor’s race. Meet the new boss.
lead_paragraph: As Alessandra Stanley wrote in Monday’s Times, the Obama administration made a point not to include Fox News in its diaspora of Sunday morning talk shows. headline.main: Middle Way Meets Fork in the Road?
